00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:48.480
ideas.

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:51.160
Advice or lessons learned.

00:08:51.160 --> 00:08:52.920
I'm going to start with the do-nots.

00:08:52.920 --> 00:08:55.480
You must have two of everything.

00:08:55.480 --> 00:08:58.220
Single points of failures will die, and you will be sad

00:08:58.220 --> 00:08:59.480
, and your users will be sad.

00:08:59.480 --> 00:09:01.710
Reputation is hard-earned and quickly lost.

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:04.000
Skip the SQLite layer in your app view.

00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:08.760
Go with my personal favorite, MySQL or Postgres,

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:12.730
if you don't like good things, and then only move

00:09:12.730 --> 00:09:14.570
past it when you're sure you need it.

